data.description: Beautiful and spacious home located in much desired Timber Oaks Subdivision! Updated and Ready for a new family! The rooms have a great flow, and the layout is fantastic. Step in and notice the large living room with large picture window, The dining room is open to the living room for those times when you need a bit more table space. granite countertops. The kitchen is open to the family room with gas fireplace. Upstairs find three bedrooms and two full baths. The primary suite has an updated bathroom that is simply lovely...The secondary bath has also been updated. Each bedroom has plentiful closet space. The partial finished basement features a large game room or playroom! Property comes with a heated above swimming pool along with huge deck! iron fenced backyard with a brick patio plus a fire-pit! The seller is leaving all decorative lighting! Quite private and the place for enjoying a hot Summer day! Conveniently located to everything...schools, shopping, parks and transportation.
